race.description: Hanlon Windows Belle Of The South Showcase
race.comment: DEEP EMOTION (8) looks ready to fire third-up. Her two runs back in town have set her up nicely for this, and his CL1 near miss at Goulburn prior to the spell reads well. Maps for a soft run and if she handles the quick turnaround, she'll take beating. PRETTY SASSY (5) has trialled twice since her 1.8L defeat in a 62 at Kembla Grange, 50-days ago. Draws inside and can't be ruled out. ABSTRUSE (9) and LETHAL LADY (2) are both Canberra-trained and have pieces of form that would see them competitive. The latter jumps from the paint and has a handy 2kg claim. MAZ KANATA (3) wasn't far away at Goulburn three back and has been very competitive on the provincial circuit recently. Back to country grade today and she rates highly.
